Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.20,0:21:20.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.38,0:21:23.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然正好是圣诞夜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.02,0:21:24.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.75,0:21:26.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶  24号啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.51,0:21:28.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我约好没有关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.42,0:21:31.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家好像都有先约了  没什么不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.19,0:21:32.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那约好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.77,0:21:33.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.62,0:21:34.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.62,0:21:37.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这么不相信我的话  要不要拉钩钩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.03,0:21:37.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.79,0:21:39.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开玩笑的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.56,0:21:40.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要啦
